    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SEARCH ALL - SEASHELLS</h2> is a game in the genre of &quot;hidden object&quot;, in which you need to find all the seashells on a large location drawn in the style of &quot;doodling&quot;. The location shows an underwater city. In the foreground of the location are large corals and an underwater castle. Behind these objects there is a huge whale and three other unusual buildings. A submarine is floating in the background, carrying the collected cargo. From the animated graphic elements in the game there are algae, a submarine, lanterns, as well as air bubbles coming from the bottom. Periodically, a variety of jellyfish swim up and down.<br><br><strong>Key Features:</strong><br>- Animation elements on location;<br>- &quot;Doodling&quot; design style;<br>- 80 seashells to find;<br>- Pleasant soundtrack:<br>- The gameplay can be interrupted at any time, and the game will automatically save the result.",
